data.description: Beautifully well kept home in the NorthEast Crossing community. The living room features nice Oak laminate flooring and a fireplace that add warmth to the very large living area. The kitchen has attractive tile flooring, granite counters, and rich wood cabinetry. Finally, the home has excellent tile work in all of the home's showers. Come view this home and make it your own.
